data.description: Inviting Colonial on the border of Elmora & Linden just waiting to be turned into a home again! First floor features a living room with wood burning stove, formal dining room, a large bedroom, kitchen with granite counter tops, a half bath and access to the back yard. Second floor features an additional 3 bedrooms with high ceilings and good closet space & a full bathroom. The full basement is ready to be finished to your liking. This is an approved short sale and an as-is sale.
